plicated for nearly three decades our investment team has cultivated these deeprooted unique local relationships we believe the combination of our panemerging markets expertise and local market relationships give gramercy a distinct advantage in emerging markets featured news gramercys chief investment officer robert koenigsberger speaks with bloomberg about investment opportunities in latin america here latin america bloomberg briefs bloomberg november   terms and conditions contact us privacy policy copyright   gramercy all rights reserved gramercy funds management llc private company information  bloomberg july    pm et capital markets company overview of gramercy funds management llc snapshot people company overview gramercy funds management llc is an employee owned hedge fund sponsor it provides its services to pooled investment vehicles pension plans foundations public retirement funds endowments high net worth investors pooled investment funds other investment advisors and corporations the firm manages separate clientfocused portfolios it also manages hedge funds for its clients the firm invests in public equity fixed income and alternative investment markets across the globe primarily in emerging countries for its debt investments it employs longonly debt strategy for its equity investments the firm employs a long only equity strategy for its alternative investments it invests in gramercy funds management llc is an employee owned hedge fund sponsor it provides its services to pooled investment vehicles pension plans foundations public retirement funds endowments high net worth investors pooled investment funds other investment advisors and corporations the firm manages separate clientfocused portfolios it also manages hedge funds for its clients the firm invests in public equity fixed income and alternative investment markets across the globe primarily in emerging countries for its debt investments it employs longonly debt strategy for its equity investments the firm employs a long only equity strategy for its alternative investments it invests in emerging markets distressed debt and special situations the firm employs fundamental analysis along with bottomup stock picking approach to create its portfolios gramercy funds management llc was founded in  and is based in greenwich connecticut with offices in london united kingdom hong kong singapore mexico city mexico and silicon valley california detailed description  dayton avenuegreenwich ct united statesfounded in  phone  wwwgramercycom key executives for gramercy funds management llc mr robert scott koenigsberger managing partner chief investment officer and emerging markets distressed portfolio manager mr robert michael joannou cpa managing director and chief financial officer mr scott guy seaman cpa partner and chief operating officer mr michael harris managing director and chief technology officer mr robert john lanava partner chief compliance officer and head of operations compensation as of fiscal year  gramercy funds management llc key developments gramercy funds management llc appoints bradshaw mckee as managing director capital solutions and distressed portfolio manager feb   gramercy funds management llc announced the appointment of bradshaw mckee to the position of managing director capital solutions and distressed portfolio manager mr mckee has over  years of distressed and structured credit experience in emerging markets he most recently coheaded emerging markets structured credit trading at deutsche bank prior to joining gramercy mr mckee was managing director global cohead of emerging markets structured credit trading at deutsche bank gramercy funds management llc names chris tackney as managing director and cohead of the gramercy trading desk aug   gramercy funds management llc announced that chris tackney has joined the firm as managing director and cohead of the gramercy trading desk mr tackney has over  years of trading and portfolio management experience in emerging markets and will cohead the trading desk with matt maloney managing director in this new role mr tackney along with mr maloney will manage a dynamic trading desk that encompasses performing and distressed corporates sovereigns equities credit default swaps and currency hedges he will also serve as a member of the investment committee prior to joining gramercy mr tackney was managing director head of trading at greylock capital before greylock mr tackney was senior portfolio manager for emerging market corporate bonds at schroder investment management with responsibility for global em corporate investments czech government considering options for okd apr   the czech government is considering taking over okd as the production subsidiary of new world resources plc lsenwr as an option to prevent the companys collapse ministers said principal creditors and owners of nwr have asked the state to help to restructure the mining group but the government has been reluctant to provide aid to okd whose previous owners paid out dividends leveraged it and split off noncore assets but it also fears that if the mining group collapses this could hurt the economy it would be ideal for okd to continue operating without problems laying off minimum number of miners and for the current owners and creditors to leave finance minister andrej babis told reporters after a cabinet meeting that discussed the situation he said owners could hand over okd and creditors sell their debt for minimum amount other options ranged from insolvency to some form of debt reduction he said industry minister jan mladek said he had offered the firms main owners and creditors known as ahg to sell the firm and its debt at a meeting with ahg last week but ahg declined to quote a price it would seek ahg includes ashmore investment management limited gramercy funds management llc and mg investment management limited an ahg spokesman had no response to the ministers statements similar private compani